## Getting started

### Hello world

```elixir
# hello.exs
defmodule Greeter do
  def greet(name) do
    message = "Hello, " <> name <> "!"
    IO.puts message
  end
end

Greeter.greet("world")
```

```bash
elixir hello.exs
# Hello, world!
```

